                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820911-23-off118 t17820911-23-cd119"></join> last, one wooden portmanteau, value 5 s. one gold watch, value 15 l. one chrystal seal set in gold, value 30 s. four muslin aprons, value 25 s. one bombazeen petticoat, value 20 s. one pair of stays, value 20 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17820911-23-victim321" type="victimName">
