                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820911-23-defend319 t17820911-23-punish123"></join>
               Transportation to America for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
